snippet.title: Exo One - Xbox Series X Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Exo One is an interplanetary journey through space and time.

Coming to Xbox Series X and Windows in 2020.

Originally premiered at the Xbox Games Showcase.

Find out more about Exo One www.exo-one-game.com
Follow the development https://twitter.com/jayweston
